      h4 Welcome to the Storecoin First Token Sale
      p Over the course of several years, we plan to conduct up to six mini Token Sales,
        | selling 33% of all tokens to the public.
      p Each token sale event will occur only when our team achieves a significant
        | technology milestone, grows the upcoming Storecoin Alliance, or sees adoption
        | on the Storecoin blockchain. We believe in aligning expectations of token
        | owners with our team’s ability to deliver. 
      hr
      .button-group
        button.button-next.button-primary(data-step='step-2')
          | Next
          i.ion-chevron-right
            
    .email-steps.step-2
      p We believe in aligning expectations of token owners with
        | our team’s ability to deliver. Over time, this will get us access
        | to the resources we need to bring Storecoin to the
        | mainstream.
      p If we don’t hit our milestones, then we likely won’t be able to
        | fund the development of the protocol. If we do, then we’ll be
        | able to hire the best talent in the world and become the
        | dominant blockchain protocol for franchises, chain stores,
        | sports leagues, and affiliate-based organizations -- industries
        | representing over 25% of global GDP.
      hr
      .button-group
        button.button-back.button-primary(data-step='step-1')
          i.ion-chevron-left
          | Back
        button.button-next.button-primary(data-step='step-3')
          | Next
          i.ion-chevron-right
            
    .email-steps.step-3
      p Our team has the key insights and experiences in hierarchybased
        | systems, distributed databases, enterprise software,
        | payments, network effects, token economics, blockchain
        | technology, and blockchain security to succeed.
      p We have offices in Silicon Valley and in Argentina with team
        | members working around the globe.
      hr
      .button-group
        button.button-back.button-primary(data-step='step-2')
          i.ion-chevron-left
          | Back
        button.button-next.button-primary(data-step='step-4')
          | Next
          i.ion-chevron-right
            
    .email-steps.step-4
