        | authorized 1 Billion tokens on the Storecoin blockchain.
      p(style="margin:0px;") 
        b Over time:
      ul
        li 33% of the tokens will be sold to the public
        li 33% will be allocated to founders, core developers, and team
        li 33% will be allocated for distribution to incentivize
           | participation in the Storecoin ecosystem
        li 1% will cover token sale costs
      hr
      .button-group
