        | working version of the Storecoin Whitepaper.
      p We are writing code, writing documentation, modeling our
        | underlying cryptoeconomics, and running extensive security
        | tests to finish the first version now.
      p The $150,000 in storecoins that we expect to sell in this First
        | Token Sale will fund our continued research and
        | development costs.
      hr
